snippet.title: Britney Spears Calls Out Christina Aguilera for Not Speaking Out about Conservatorship
snippet.description:
Britney Spears called Christina Aguilera out for not speaking up about the singer’s freedom now that her controversial conservatorship has ended. Tell us: Was Britney out of line for expecting Christina to speak out?
